title: Samurai #01 (1986) Barry Blair-Aircel
description:
one of the flagship titles from Aircel and the one I find surprisingly missing from the Aircel torrent floating around

this is just the first issue and i'm having a difficult time trying to photoshop the other issues due to the ink wash style that was used and the crappy paper it was printed on.

if anyone has any ideas/tips/guides to help facilitate the process it would be much appreciated.

Thanks

Enjoy
